Burlington Industries Inc file Securities Exchange Commission registration statement cover offering debt securities. One issue 100 mln dlrs sinking fund debenture due 2017. Proceeds corporate purpose include reduction short-term borrowing acquisition stock repurchase capital expenditures. The offering 75 mln dlrs convertible subordinate debenture due 2012. Proceeds redeem company's outstanding 8-3/4 pct convertible subordinate debenture 2008 Burlington said. Reuter 